        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/25/28",
        "text": [
          "٢٥. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): يَابْنَ آدَمَ، إِذَا رَأَيْتَ رَبَّكَ سُبْحَانَهُ يُتَابِعُ عَلَيْكَ نِعَمَهُ وَأَنْتَ تَعْصِيهِ فَاحْذَرْهُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "25. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: O son of Adam, when you see that your Lord, the Glorified, bestows His favours on you while you are disobeying Him, you should fear Him. [1]"
          ]
        }
      }
